  <title>Delete a note</title>    
  
  <p>You can delete a note by pressing the <gui>Delete</gui> icon in the toolbar of the note you wish to delete.</p>
  
<note style="tip">
	<p>Deleting a note is permanent.  You will be prompted "Really delete this note?" when deleting a note and 
	after deletion the note is not recoverable.</p>
</note>
	
